I"¿<ol>
  <li>Download &amp; install <a href="https://www.silabs.com/Support%20Documents/Software/Mac_OSX_VCP_Driver.zip">OS X Driver</a>.</li>
  <li>On the <em>Raspbian</em> <code class="highlighter-rouge">boot</code> partition, add these lines to <code class="highlighter-rouge">config.txt</code> to enable UART:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>enable_uart=1
dtoverlay=pi3-disable-bt
</code></pre></div>    </div>

    <blockquote>
      <p><strong>Note</strong>: To enable the serial console, Bluetooth will be disabled!</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
  <li>In <code class="highlighter-rouge">cmdline.txt</code> change <code class="highlighter-rouge">console=tty1</code> to <code class="highlighter-rouge">console=ttyAMA0</code>.</li>
  <li>Connect <a href="https://www.amazon.de/gp/product/B00AFRXKFU">CP2102</a> to Raspberry Pi CPIO pins (bottom right):
    <blockquote>
      <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
                      Pin  10 8 6   2
                            | | |   | 
                           TXD|GND  5V
                             RXD
</code></pre></div>      </div>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
  <li>Connect to serial console:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>screen /dev/tty.SLAB_USBtoUART 115200
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Press <code class="highlighter-rouge">[ctrl+a]</code>, <code class="highlighter-rouge">k</code>, <code class="highlighter-rouge">y</code> to exit <code class="highlighter-rouge">screen</code>.</li>
</ol>

